content: व्यक्त {%<ab>p. p.</ab>%} {@--1@} Manifested, displayed. {@--2@} Developed, created; <ls>Ku. 2. 11.</ls> {@--3@} Evident, manifest, clear, plain, distinct, clearly visible; <ls>Pt. 2. 92.</ls> {@--4@} Specified, known, distinguished. {@--5@} Individual. {@--6@} Wise, learned. {@--7@} <ab>Ved.</ab> Adorned, decorated. --क्तः <ab>N.</ab> of Viṣṇu. --क्तं That which is developed as the product of अव्यक्त <ab>q. v.</ab> --क्तं {%<ab>ind.</ab>%} Clearly, evidently, certainly.
